    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You want to use the <code>yyyy</code> year and <code>dd</code> day of the month.</p>\n\n<p>However, I suggest you migrate to JSR-310 which is built into Java 8 and available for earlier versions of Java.  The same code is</p>\n\n<pre><code>System.out.println(LocalDate.now());\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>prints</p>\n\n<pre><code>2105-02-02\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
